When working on **grammar**, **lexis**, or **phonology** (English learning data):

- **Content domain names**: Use only **grammar**, **lexis**, **phonology** for
  structural names. No synonyms (e.g. vocabulary,
  pronunciation, phonics). See `shared/context/documentation/MANUAL.md` §
  Naming conventions → Content domain names.
- **Seed/infra**: Source metadata seed lives under **material** (`shared/infra/seed/material/`, `deno task seed:material`); env vars `SOURCE_META_*`. Subdomain is material, not lexis.
- **Difficulty / level**: Use **basic**, **intermediate**, **advanced** (lowercase
  everywhere). See MANUAL.md § Naming conventions → Difficulty / level (3
  stages).
